<br>
I just finished reading all 10! pages to this thread, and I wanted to make a comment that may be useful in your arguement.<br>
<br>
First of all, I'm 100% in favor of right click nuke items. They very effeciently smooth out the DPS curve, while not being overpowering.  (assuming of course there are sensible lvl restrictions)<br>
<br>
The primary objection to this however, is that according to the &quot;Vision&quot; wizards are a burst damage class and not a sustained damage class.  As such, VI may reject any arguement that attempts to improve wizard sustained DPS.  They may argue that wizard balancing should only consists of tweaks to burst DPS.  I do not believe this is fair to the wizard class.<br>
<br>
